   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Argenta.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-1-a" mid="18" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Argenta$<BR>So did you manage find anything at all?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Arno.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-1-b" mid="20" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Arno${sound:npc_Arno_9417_qu_01.ogg}<BR>We have decided to erect a seal stone.<BR>A seal stone that is strong enough to contain your powers.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Argenta.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-1-c" mid="22" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Argenta$<BR>A seal stone…? You want it to contain my powers?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Arno.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-1-d" mid="24" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Arno$<BR>Yes. If we build a seal stone near the Monolith's door and fill it with your power, you don't have to disappear. The seal stone will keep the Monolith closed. Unless the seal stone is destroyed, no one in Lagendia would be able to open the Monolith.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Argenta.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-1-e" mid="26" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Argenta${sound:npc_Argenta_9417_qu_01.ogg}<BR>Hmm... that's not a bad idea. But how are you going to create a seal stone like that?<BR>I'm a dragon. It's not easy for you to create something that can contain my power.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Argenta.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-1-f" mid="28" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Argenta$<BR>Moreover, there is no time.<BR>Though the effects of the open Monolith seem slow right now, it will soon speed up and destroy the world.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Argenta.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-1-g" mid="30" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Argenta$<BR>I'll praise you a little for all the effort you must have put in to come up with this plan.<BR>But it's too late. This world has to recover to a certain degree for you to collect enough materials to build the stone. That would take too much time.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Arno.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-1-h" mid="32" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Arno$<BR>...not necessarily.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-1-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Argenta.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-1-i" mid="34" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$Argenta$<BR>What?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-1-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Arno.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-1-j" mid="36" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$Arno$<BR>You said we have three days. One day has passed, and we have two more days. I can make it within these two days.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-1-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Argenta.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-1-k" mid="38" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Argenta$<BR>HAHA! Two days?? That's impossible. You're not the Goddess.<BR>You can't make a seal stone that can contain my powers within just TWO days!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-1-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Arno.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-1-l" mid="40" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Arno$<BR>This world needs you more than you think. We are doing this to beg for your forgiveness, so please show your mercy...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-1-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Arno.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-1-m" mid="42" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>$Arno${action:Talk}<BR>Please don't forget that we are the ones who read the Goddess's dreams.<BR>We may have more knowledge then you think. It's just that we were too foolish...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-1-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Argenta.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-2" mid="44" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$Argenta$<BR>Action is what counts, not words. I'll trust you a little on this one. Two days is all you have.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Argenta.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-2-" mid="46" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>$Argenta${sound:npc_Argenta_9417_qu_02.ogg}<BR>I will not forgive you if you do something foolish again.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
