      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-3-b" mid="52" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="51"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(That's... Gaharam?? What is she doing here?!)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Gaharam.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-3-b" mid="54" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="53"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Teacher?? What is she doing here?!)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-3-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Gaharam.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-3-c" mid="56" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="55"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam${sound:npc_Gaharam_9417_qu_01.ogg}<BR>Father, I heard your conversation with the Silver Dragon. What are you planning to do...?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-3-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Arno.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-3-d" mid="58" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="57"><![CDATA[<html>$Arno${sound:npc_Arno_9417_qu_02.ogg}<BR>Gaharam, my child.<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Arno smiles)</FONT><BR>Which part did you hear?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-3-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Arno.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-3-e" mid="60" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="59"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Father...? Arno was Gaharam's father???</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-3-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Gaharam.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-3-f" mid="62" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="61"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam${sound:npc_Gaharam_9417_qu_02.ogg}<BR>I heard everything. I've never heard about seal stones before. We've already spent too much energy on the Mirror of Truth. How can we make something that can hold Argenta's powers?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-3-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Gaharam.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-3-g" mid="64" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="63"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam${sound:npc_Gaharam_9417_qu_03.ogg}{action:Talk}<BR>We have to wait for a long time to collect that kind of power. Father... it's impossible.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-3-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Arno.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-3-h" mid="66" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="65"><![CDATA[<html>$Arno${sound:npc_Arno_9417_qu_03.ogg}<BR>Time is irrelevant when faced with an overpowering strength.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-3-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Gaharam.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-3-i" mid="68" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="67"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam${sound:npc_Gaharam_9417_qu_04.ogg}<BR>Father...?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-3-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Arno.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-3-j" mid="70" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="69"><![CDATA[<html>$Arno${sound:npc_Arno_9417_qu_04.ogg}<BR>How many lives were sacrificed for our sins? How devastated the world has become because of us.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-3-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Gaharam.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-3-k" mid="72" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="71"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam${sound:npc_Gaharam_9417_qu_05.ogg}<BR>That's... that's something that can never be forgiven. But you know that everyone is regretting and repenting their wrongdoings. It won't happen again.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-3-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Arno.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-3-l" mid="74" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="73"><![CDATA[<html>$Arno${sound:npc_Arno_9417_qu_05.ogg}<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Arno's eyes widen)</FONT><BR>It won't happen again?! No... I don't agree with you. My dear child, don't you realize how ugly and foolish creatures we are?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-3-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Arno.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-3-m" mid="76" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="75"><![CDATA[<html>$Arno$<BR>It seems like we are the poison and filth that is corrupting this world.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-3-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Gaharam.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-3-n" mid="78" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="77"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam$<BR>How can you say that? If we really are such creatures, we wouldn't have put our lives at stake to save you. I believe in our people. Father, why did you tell Argenta what you did?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-3-n" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Arno.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-3-o" mid="80" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="79"><![CDATA[<html>$Arno$<BR>All parents would want to save their child. My dear daughter...<BR>My plan is the only right thing we can do. It's the only way! But...!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-3-o" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Arno.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-3-p" mid="82" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="81"><![CDATA[<html>$Arno$<BR>But if I think about it... maybe there's another way. But I must be fair to everyone. For that, I must...<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Arno's eyes are shining with madness)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-3-p" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Gaharam.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-3-q" mid="84" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="83"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam$<BR>Father...?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-3-q" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Arno.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-3-r" mid="86" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="85"><![CDATA[<html>$Arno${sound:npc_Arno_9417_qu_06.ogg}<BR>I will tell you what I will do in the next two days!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-3-r" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Arno.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-3-s" mid="88" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="87"><![CDATA[<html>$Arno$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Arno whispers to Gaharam)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-3-s" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Gaharam.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-3-t" mid="90" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="89"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam${sound:npc_Gaharam_9417_qu_06.ogg}<BR>...!!<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Gaharam turns pale and steps away from her father)</FONT><BR>D-do you mean what you just said...?! Father?!?!?!?!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-3-t" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Arno.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-3-u" mid="92" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="91"><![CDATA[<html>$Arno${sound:npc_Arno_9417_qu_07.ogg}<BR>Isn't it a perfect plan? There can't be a better solution than this.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-3-u" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Gaharam.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-3-v" mid="94" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="93"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam${sound:npc_Gaharam_9417_qu_07.ogg}<BR>Father... are you mad?! That can never happen! Why do you think we survived the sacrifices and struggles until now?! You must think twice, you're not in the right mind!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-3-v" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Arno.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-3-w" mid="96" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="95"><![CDATA[<html>$Arno${sound:npc_Arno_9417_qu_08.ogg}<BR>Why can't you understand? <BR>But my last hopes are on you. You will spread our knowledge as the Prophet from now on. You will pass on our wisdom, and atone for our sins!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-3-w" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Gaharam.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-3-x" mid="98" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="97"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam${sound:npc_Gaharam_9417_qu_08.ogg}<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Gaharam cries out loud)</FONT><BR>Father!!! No!!! I don't want that!<BR>Don't do this!!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-3-x" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Arno.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-4" mid="100" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="99"><![CDATA[<html>$Arno$<BR>Please take her. Everything will follow the Goddess's will.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1526_for_memory-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Gaharam.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1526_for_memory-4-" mid="102" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="101"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam$<BR>Father! Father...! No! No!!!!!!!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1527_people-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Ancient_minion.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1527_people-4-a" mid="104" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="103"><![CDATA[<html>$Ancient 1$<BR>Arno, time has come. They are here without knowing why.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1527_people-4-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Ancient_minion.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1527_people-4-b" mid="106" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="105"><![CDATA[<html>$Ancient 2$<BR>You were right, Arno. The recent incident revealed how corrupt we truly are.<BR>The reason why the Goddess gave us so much power must be so that we can do this.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1527_people-4-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Ancient_minion.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1527_people-4-c" mid="108" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="107"><![CDATA[<html>$Ancient 3$<BR>That's right. She's allowig us to clean up the mess we've made with our own hands.<BR>And we won't be completely dead anyway.<BR>We can atone for our sins and leave hope at the same time.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1527_people-4-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Ancient_minion.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1527_people-4-d" mid="110" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="109"><![CDATA[<html>$Ancient 1$<BR>Fools would never understand even if they are persuaded day and night.<BR>They would only realize when it's too late.<BR>I never expected there would be so many fools among us...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1527_people-4-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Ancient_minion.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1527_people-4-e" mid="112" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="111"><![CDATA[<html>$Ancient 3$<BR>Almost all the Ancients across the continent have gathered.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1527_people-4-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Ancient_minion.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1527_people-5" mid="114" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="113"><![CDATA[<html>$Ancient 2$<BR>Arno, please hurry.<BR>Hurry before the foolish ones find out about your plan. We need to act swiftly.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1527_people-5" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Arno.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1527_people-5-" mid="116" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="115"><![CDATA[<html>$Arno$<BR>Very well. Let's go and show our repentance to the Goddess.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1525_aruno-5" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Arno.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1525_aruno-5-a" mid="118" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="117"><![CDATA[<html>$Arno$<BR>...I'm done with the preparation.<BR>I have ended everything... Now all my hopes will be on my daughter.<BR>Hear my prophecy. My daughter shall do many things in my name.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1525_aruno-5-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Arno.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1525_aruno-5-class_check" mid="120" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="119"><![CDATA[<html>$Arno$<BR>...I am sorry, Gaharam.<BR>I'm sorry Nereid...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1525_aruno-5-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Arno.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1525_aruno-5-c" mid="122" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="121"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(I didn't know such things happened... and... Arno was Gaharam's father!)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1525_aruno-5-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Arno.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1525_aruno-5-g" mid="124" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="123"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(But when I met Gaharam last time, she was a ghost. What happened to her?)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1525_aruno-5-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Arno.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1525_aruno-5-e" mid="126" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="125"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Teacher really is Arno's daughter…? But she was still with me not that long ago...)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1525_aruno-5-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Arno.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1525_aruno-5-f" mid="128" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="127"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Then how old is Teacher? Wait, I'm in the distant past right now so is Teacher a descendant of Gaharam? She can't still be alive after all those years.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1525_aruno-5-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Arno.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1525_aruno-5-g" mid="130" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="129"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(...But she looks the same… exactly the same...)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1525_aruno-5-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Arno.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1525_aruno-5-h" mid="132" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="131"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(The slate glows again. This time, it's pointing to the Abyss of Heat.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
